n    \"_file\": \"meta.json\"\n  },\n  \"output\": {}\n}\n```\n\nSuccess hint: when `output/unite_stats.tsv` exists under the workspace, you may call submit_done(success=true).\n"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_RyUWF1Z8EFoLBZd7pmiqwmHS", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"plan\": \"1. Load the methylation data from the four coverage files using `methylKit::methRead` with the specified parameters.\\n2. Unite the methylation data using `methylKit::unite` with the specified parameters.\\n3. Save the united methylBase object to `output/mk_united.rds` using `saveRDS`.\\n4. Create a single-row table with the specified statistics and save it to `output/unite_stats.tsv` using `write_tsv`.\\n5. Verify the existence of `output/unite_stats.tsv` and call `submit_done(success=true)` if it exists.\"}", "name": "write_plan"}}]}, {"role": "tool", "content": "Wrote plan (503 chars) to .plan.md", "name": "write_plan", "tool_call_id": "call_RyUWF1Z8EFoLBZd7pmiqwmHS"}, {"role": "assistant", "content": null, "function_call": null, "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_VKOTReb4iAiKVmNtHcDTJwEb", "type": "function", "function": {"arguments": "{\"code\": \"library(methylKit)\\n\\n# Load the methylation data\\nfile.list <- list(\\n  'input/sampleA.bismark.cov',\\n  'input/sampleB.bismark.cov',\\n  'input/sampleC.bismark.cov',\\n  'input/sampleD.bismark.cov'\\n)\\n\\nmk_raw <- methRead(\\n  file.list,\\n  sample.id = c('sampleA', 'sampleB', 'sampleC', 'sampleD'),\\n  assembly = 'mock_v1',\\n  pipeline = 'bismarkCoverage',\\n  treatment = c(0, 0, 1, 1),\\n  mincov = 4\\n)\\n\\n# Unite the methylation data\\nmk_united <- unite(mk_raw, min.per.group = 1, destrand = FALSE)\\n\\n# Save the united methylBase object\\nsaveRDS(mk_united, 'output/mk_united.rds')\\n\\n# Create the unite_stats.tsv file\\nn_samples <- length(mk_united@sample.ids)\\nn_sites <- nrow(mk_united@.Data[[1]])\\nmin_per_group <- 1\\ndestrand <- FALSE\\nuse_db <- 